===Etymology===
Compare Gamilaraay ''[[tharra#Gamilaraay|tharra]]'' and Wangaaybuwan-Ngiyambaa ''[[tharra#Wangaaybuwan-Ngiyambaa|tharra]]''.
===Noun===
'''dharrang'''

# [[thigh]]
